PRESERVE FOOD: Storing food without refrigeration

Category: Domestic
Base skill: 25% (+5%/level, cap 98%)

Preserving food for the long term without refrigeration or modern
equipment: salting, smoking, drying, and similar methods. Valuable
knowledge anywhere reliable power and preservation technology cannot
be counted on.

NOTES:
  No AetherMUD command currently rolls this skill directly. It is
  available for character concept and staff-adjudicated roleplay.

SEE ALSO: skills, cook, wilderness survival
